{"tid":19151,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"淫蕩俏老師寄猥褻照　教室內課輔口愛 被控2級性騷擾罪","createTime":"2016-12-02T16:07:09.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-03T02:00:16.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"58108a54a84bf16eba7fbad2fce175c90b17ab98","tid":19151,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T16:07:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20161201/640_549000da270ea4ca207fe9b131c2b9a9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20161201%2F640_549000da270ea4ca207fe9b131c2b9a9.jpg&h=5e465ca0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n淫蕩俏老師馬琪絲寄猥褻照給學生，還在教室內課輔口愛。翻自《鏡報》<br />\n<br />\n美國康乃狄克州一名39歲英文女老師馬琪絲(Allison Marchese)，在丹尼爾韓德高中(Daniel Hand High School)任職期間，涉嫌對2名男學生寄猥褻照、傳情色簡訊，甚至在教室內對其中一名學生進行「口交課輔」。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《鏡報》報導，馬琪絲從前年開始看上兩名學生，其中一名才年僅14歲。馬琪絲先是約他們出來吃午餐，然後說：「你們長得好帥，害我上課沒辦法專心。」然後學生回應「請老師自重」，但馬琪絲卻說「你讓我好傷心，你背叛了我」。另外一名現年17歲的男學生說，馬琪絲不斷傳給他色情簡訊和猥褻照，兩人甚至在一間教室內進行口交，但該名學生也承認，曾經要利用這段醜聞，計畫向馬琪絲勒索200美金(約新台幣6000元)。<br />\n<br />\n目前馬琪絲被控犯下第2級性騷擾罪與性危害，最高恐被判20年徒刑，預計全案將在明年3月宣判。<br />\n台灣網友則認為：「我怎麼遇不到這種老師呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」、「不用衝著我來嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」、「老師只是上健康教育操作課程。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」、「要是我有個這麼善解人意的老實，我的青春就不會如此悶悶不樂了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20161201/640_90ea54932ff9db5c168a979110528c90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20161201%2F640_90ea54932ff9db5c168a979110528c90.jpg&h=fdf55c27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n馬琪絲傳給學生的猥褻照。翻自《鏡報》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20161201/640_7e0e8b0ce7e179e05fe5c4ea11e2649a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20161201%2F640_7e0e8b0ce7e179e05fe5c4ea11e2649a.jpg&h=143a6a5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n馬琪絲最高恐被判20年徒刑。翻自《鏡報》"},{"pid":"e5ec582c347a70fe407bcf0f6eafa97d84c0dfb0","tid":19151,"uid":7961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T16:08:32.000Z","msg":"有講過"},{"pid":"0f14126c6b7eb0e0067f042d803c3030abd7cab7","tid":19151,"uid":21707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T16:08:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">施旖婕</span></span>"},{"pid":"fbec8e698fb66097676d80ffb2d994798bde5dad","tid":19151,"uid":35094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T16:08:55.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"99965168066e0453e949321af78aebb5e1b8f4df","tid":19151,"uid":36440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T16:10:04.000Z","msg":"屌，D台仔重口味到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3db28f846a297f36ff6e4333301454944ee03298","tid":19151,"uid":26047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T16:10:30.000Z","msg":"有咩事我頂 放過班學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd8722d071dc87feaa2655f86644daa5be4a6dca","tid":19151,"uid":39838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T16:11:38.000Z","msg":"39歲鬼婆雖然樣好似ok但我咩都無講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f1ba9bea6bf02a25b1efe718f46d420fab5fa1e","tid":19151,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T16:17:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55f317e17d1be682a51f4cd47cfc2d6402ce26a9","tid":19151,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T17:25:14.000Z","msg":"樓下有講過"},{"pid":"a8cac66cf7120910169